name: Lisa
about: Hi, I'm Lisa, a Hip-Hop teacher with many years of experience. I teach fun and inclusive classes that focus on building technique and individual expression. Join me to learn new moves, build your confidence, and connect with other Hip-Hop lovers. Let's dance!

name: Kazuha
about: Hi, I'm Kazuha, a ballet instructor with 10 years of experience. I teach students of all levels the fundamental principles of ballet, emphasizing technical excellence and artistic expression. Join me in a supportive and inclusive environment to build your confidence, creativity, and grace as a ballet artist.

name: Chungha
about: Hey there, I'm Chungha, a Waacking dance instructor with 3 of experience. In my classes, I teach the techniques and style of Waacking, emphasizing musicality and expression. Join me in a fun and supportive environment to learn new moves, build your skills, and explore your creativity. Let's discover the joy and freedom of Waacking dance together!
